Welcome to the start of the 2009 Championship tournament. The top 16 wrestlers of the season face off in a single elimination tournament. Check out the Summer Vengeance Bracket here.
Annie Cruz finished this year ranked 15th, she is a veteran of many seasons but has yet to win a tournament match up. This sexy Asian never gives up and fights to the last whistle.
Claire Dames was a rookie this year and got the last spot on the roster. Her massive boobs and her determination to win has made her a fan favorite.
This is the kick-off match for this years single elimination tournament. Join now and experience the action from the start!
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE TOURNAMENT MATCH UP!
